channel.title: //** RSC 4 True F2P-Pkers **\\// 24/7 Up Time \\// Join Today \\ New Landscaping
channel.description:
We are back up F2P Style!
getRecentUpdates() { Change client size in gamewidth.ini New Landscape for edgeville Nearly EVERYTHING you need to PK is all in edgeville. Shops, NPCs added to edgeville!
Administrators/Moderators can't attack or be attacked Pk Points added, if you Kill you gain 2, if you die you lose 1. (Note you only lose Pk Points if you have > 0 (greater than 0)). KillSpree added, if you Kill you gain 1, if you die you lose all. Added ::wild command, shows how much players are in the wilderness. Added a boolean so P2P items cannot be worn. NPC's now face you when you talk to them. Resizable client. Most common DCs fixed (I guarantee you will DC rarely unless you have crap internet connection). }
F2P-Pkers is new to the community We are just trying to get a even amount of players that love Pking F2P Style All new players are welcome. You will find more to do once you get playing. Updates will be daily with lots of new updates available in the next couple days You guys will not be dissopointed this time around. You will not DC and if you do it will be RARE
Our XP rates are currently at 70x
Website: http://f2p-pkers.sytes.net/ Client Mirror: http://www.mediafire.com/?ymywjnybmqz
We hope to see you online and have fun, our staff treat players how they want to be treated them self, so be nice and you will get the same respect back.
